summary: this is my first mod. it's a simple bat file that gives the player character all perks, spells, dragon  shouts, high stamina, and magicka and a million in gold
descriptionHtml: This mod is for players that have already played the game and don't want the hassle of leveling up when starting a new game. To activate in game just drag and drop from zip into your skyrim/data folder, pull up your console command with ~ in game and type "bat c". simple and easy. all vanilla spells, shouts, and perks along with high stamina and magicka. also 1 million in gold will be yours. have fun.
author: quon200
